headline: Hilton Lands in DHS Crosshairs After ICE Agents’ Hotel Reservations Are Canceled
summary: The alleged campaign against law enforcement descending on Minneapolis has reignited the debate over when a business can refuse service.

headline: Hilton shares fall after DHS says Minneapolis hotel canceled reservation due to immigration enforcement
summary: "We are not allowing any ICE or immigration agents to stay at our property," an email cited by DHS said.
